> Are you sure it is ThreadLocalMap? I looked at the code you wrote and found that ThreadLocalMap was not used.   

It's  `org.apache.dubbo.common.threadlocal.InternalThreadLocalMap` used, 
We can use `jcmd <pid> GC.class_histogram|grep "InternalThreadLocalMap"` to see the instances.  
And you can add 
````
                InternalThreadLocalMap.getIfSet().indexedVariable(0);
                InternalThreadLocalMap.getIfSet().indexedVariable(1);
                InternalThreadLocalMap.getIfSet().indexedVariable(2);
                InternalThreadLocalMap.getIfSet().indexedVariable(3);
````
